{"tid":2508792,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"DSE 2021｜中文閱讀卷首現日本文學　引芥川龍之介《橘子》出題","createTime":"2021-04-29T04:26:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-29T07:18:59.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"7d1f067a9b04ec93d2a4bf8d86b132f667eb41c3","tid":2508792,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T04:26:49.000Z","msg":"中學文憑試閱讀及寫作卷今日開考。卷一閱讀卷甲部範文考核《消遙遊》、《魚我所欲也》、《論仁、論孝、論君子》及《念奴嬌&middot;赤壁懷古》。<br />\n<br />\n乙部課外篇章方面，則有三篇，分別是台灣作家徐國能《火車和橘子》、日本作家芥川龍之介、內地翻譯家文潔若譯的《橘子》、文言文《說苑‧立節》。<br />\n<br />\n中學文憑試中文科閱讀卷2018年起，增設12篇範文，即指定文言經典學習材料，佔試卷分數30%，即佔中文科總分約7%。<br />\n<br />\n閱讀卷甲部的指定閱讀篇章考核包括，《消遙遊》、《魚我所欲也》、《論仁、論孝、論君子》及《念奴嬌&middot;赤壁懷古》。<br />\n<br />\n乙部課外篇章方面，則有三篇，包括台灣作家徐國能《火車和橘子》、日本作家芥川龍之介、內地翻譯家文潔若譯的《橘子》、文言文《說苑‧立節》。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210429/464379197255585792896342.jpeg/AEEHd0DaRDs9ouqX4LbpIKJ-9m2H2Z6_x6DEx8egxMc?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210429%2F464379197255585792896342.jpeg%2FAEEHd0DaRDs9ouqX4LbpIKJ-9m2H2Z6_x6DEx8egxMc%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=51e69e65&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fea5f3f63a1c612d032e9e1781667e4027ebb82a","tid":2508792,"uid":189996,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T04:32:11.000Z","msg":"橘子係咪個女仔拋橘子出火車嗰篇<br />\n記得以前老師教過<br />\n<br />\n利申 老鬼"},{"pid":"352309cfa7c201c2bc11aba43750a05686b1ae0b","tid":2508792,"uid":145273,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T04:41:32.000Z","msg":"做咩今年兩篇白話文都係同橙有關<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70cdaba0f0315265422ade598566b5a7371d5a6d","tid":2508792,"uid":8014,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"reply